00:40:30,528 --> 00:40:33,564
I curse you to spend all your money
and go bankrupt!

528
00:40:33,631 --> 00:40:36,234
Get fat and die from high cholesterol!

529
00:40:36,301 --> 00:40:38,269
And go to hell after you die!

530
00:40:38,336 --> 00:40:40,305
Especially Pig Head 4!

531
00:40:40,371 --> 00:40:42,840
Your bodies will be ripped apart
by horses in the end!

532
00:40:44,709 --> 00:40:45,843
And then?

533
00:40:48,379 --> 00:40:49,681
Why are you here?

534
00:40:52,717 --> 00:40:54,018
You can bully me.

535
00:40:54,786 --> 00:40:56,120
However, you have to wait a bit.

536
00:40:57,655 --> 00:40:58,823
I have to rest first.

537
00:41:05,296 --> 00:41:06,297
Wipe yourself clean.

538
00:41:27,051 --> 00:41:28,186
Thank you.

539
00:41:32,991 --> 00:41:35,259
I'm sorry I said those things earlier.

540
00:41:35,994 --> 00:41:37,161
Because I was just...

541
00:41:37,228 --> 00:41:38,529
It doesn't matter.

542
00:41:39,897 --> 00:41:42,166
I'm not interested
in other people's business.

543
00:41:43,968 --> 00:41:45,536
Hey, your handkerchief.

544
00:41:46,137 --> 00:41:48,539
Throw it away.
It's already garbage anyway.

545
00:41:55,813 --> 00:41:57,081
Silly me.

546
00:41:57,148 --> 00:41:59,584
I thought he's different
from the other three.

547
00:41:59,650 --> 00:42:01,285
I'm such an idiot.

548
00:42:32,884 --> 00:42:35,486
I have good news and bad news.

549
00:42:36,020 --> 00:42:37,922
The good news is,

550
00:42:37,989 --> 00:42:39,824
your endurance earned my respect.

551
00:42:40,191 --> 00:42:41,659
The bad news is,

552
00:42:41,726 --> 00:42:43,861
I'll work even harder to bully you.

553
00:44:44,448 --> 00:44:46,517
